steps {
  type: CORTEX_STEP_TYPE_USER_INPUT
  status: CORTEX_STEP_STATUS_DONE
  metadata {
    created_at {
      seconds: 1780721870
      nanos: 307667829
    }
    source: CORTEX_STEP_SOURCE_USER_EXPLICIT
  }
  user_input {
    user_response: "Act as a Senior Android UI/UX Designer and Senior Android Developer.\n\nGenerate a complete Android application UI design using Material Design 3 for the project:\n\n# AI-Powered Cleaning Service Booking Platform\n\nA mobile application that allows customers to book cleaning services, workers to accept jobs, and administrators to manage the entire platform. The system integrates AI Chatbot, AI Worker Recommendation, Online Payment, Real-time Notifications, GPS Tracking, and Authentication.\n\n## Design Requirements\n\n* Platform: Android\n* Design System: Material Design 3\n* Style: Modern, Professional, Clean, Similar to Grab, Uber, Airbnb and Shopee\n* Responsive Mobile UI\n* Support Dark Mode\n* Smooth animations\n* Production-ready design\n* Use realistic data\n* Generate UI hierarchy and screen layout descriptions\n* Generate Jetpack Compose UI structure for each screen\n\nPrimary Color: #2563EB\n\nSecondary Color: #10B981\n\nAccent Color: #F59E0B\n\n---\n\n# USER ROLES\n\n1. Client\n2. Worker\n3. Admin\n\n---\n\n# AUTHENTICATION MODULE\n\nCreate screens:\n\n1. Splash Screen\n2. Onboarding Screen (3 Slides)\n3. Login Screen\n4. Register Screen\n5. Forgot Password Screen\n6. OTP Verification Screen\n7. Reset Password Screen\n\nInclude:\n\n* Validation states\n* Loading states\n* Error states\n* Success states\n\n---\n\n# CLIENT APPLICATION\n\nBottom Navigation:\n\n* Home\n* Bookings\n* AI Chat\n* Notifications\n* Profile\n\n---\n\n# HOME SCREEN\n\nSections:\n\n* Welcome Header\n* Search Bar\n* Promotional Banner Carousel\n* Service Categories Grid\n* Popular Services\n* Nearby Workers\n* AI Recommended Workers\n* Special Offers\n\nService Categories:\n\n* House Cleaning\n* Deep Cleaning\n* Sofa Cleaning\n* Carpet Cleaning\n* Office Cleaning\n* Air Conditioner Cleaning\n\n---\n\n# SERVICE DETAIL SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Service Image\n* Service Name\n* Description\n* Price\n* Duration\n* Reviews\n* Ratings\n* Book Now Button\n\n---\n\n# CREATE BOOKING FLOW\n\nStep 1:\nSelect Service\n\nStep 2:\nSelect Address\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Google Maps\n* Current Location\n* Saved Addresses\n\nStep 3:\nChoose Date & Time\n\nStep 4:\nAdditional Notes\n\nStep 5:\nBooking Summary\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Price Breakdown\n* Service Fee\n* Additional Fee\n* Total Price\n\nButton:\nConfirm Booking\n\n---\n\n# AI WORKER MATCHING SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\nWorker Cards with:\n\n* Avatar\n* Name\n* Rating\n* Distance\n* Experience\n* Match Percentage\n* AI Recommendation Explanation\n\nActions:\n\n* View Profile\n* Assign Worker\n\n---\n\n# BOOKING DETAIL SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Booking Information\n* Booking Timeline\n* Current Status\n* Live Map Tracking\n* Worker Information\n* Call Worker\n* Chat Worker\n* Invoice\n* Payment Status\n\nActions:\n\n* Cancel Booking\n* Rebook Service\n\n---\n\n# PAYMENT MODULE\n\nSupported Methods:\n\n* Cash\n* MoMo\n* VNPay\n* ZaloPay\n* Bank Transfer\n\nScreens:\n\n* Payment Method Selection\n* Payment Confirmation\n* Payment Success\n* Payment Failed\n\n---\n\n# REVIEW MODULE\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Worker Information\n* Rating Stars\n* Comment Box\n* Photo Upload\n\nAction:\n\nSubmit Review\n\n---\n\n# AI CHATBOT MODULE\n\nDesign a ChatGPT-like interface.\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Chat Messages\n* AI Suggestions\n* Voice Input\n* Typing Indicator\n* Suggested Questions\n\nExample Suggestions:\n\n* How much does house cleaning cost?\n* Find workers near me\n* Recommend a cleaning package\n\n---\n\n# NOTIFICATION MODULE\n\nTabs:\n\n* All\n* Unread\n* Booking Updates\n* Promotions\n* AI Recommendations\n\nInclude:\n\n* Empty State\n* Read/Unread State\n\n---\n\n# PROFILE MODULE\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Avatar\n* Full Name\n* Email\n* Phone Number\n\nSections:\n\n* Edit Profile\n* Addresses\n* Payment Methods\n* Booking History\n* Support Center\n* Settings\n* Logout\n\n---\n\n# ADDRESS MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Add Address\n* Edit Address\n* Delete Address\n* Set Default Address\n* Map Picker\n\n---\n\n# WORKER APPLICATION\n\nCreate dedicated worker screens.\n\nWorker Bottom Navigation:\n\n* Dashboard\n* Jobs\n* Schedule\n* Wallet\n* Profile\n\n---\n\n# WORKER DASHBOARD\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Today\'s Earnings\n* Weekly Earnings\n* Monthly Earnings\n* Rating\n* Completed Jobs\n\nCharts:\n\n* Earnings Chart\n* Performance Chart\n\n---\n\n# WORKER JOB LIST\n\nTabs:\n\n* New Jobs\n* Accepted\n* In Progress\n* Completed\n\nActions:\n\n* Accept Job\n* Reject Job\n\n---\n\n# WORKER JOB DETAIL\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Customer Information\n* Address\n* Route Map\n* Service Details\n\nActions:\n\n* Start Job\n* Complete Job\n* Upload Before/After Images\n\n---\n\n# WORKER SCHEDULE SCREEN\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Calendar View\n* Upcoming Jobs\n* Availability Toggle\n\n---\n\n# WORKER WALLET SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Balance\n* Earnings\n* Withdraw Button\n* Transaction History\n\n---\n\n# WORKER PROFILE SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Avatar\n* Identity Verification\n* Skills\n* Certificates\n* Ratings\n* Reviews\n\n---\n\n# ADMIN APPLICATION\n\nCreate admin dashboard screens.\n\n---\n\n# ADMIN DASHBOARD\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Total Users\n* Total Workers\n* Total Bookings\n* Revenue\n* AI Requests\n\nCharts:\n\n* Revenue Trend\n* Booking Trend\n* User Growth\n\n---\n\n# USER MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Search\n* Filter\n* User Detail\n* Ban User\n* Activate User\n\n---\n\n# WORKER MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Verify Worker\n* Approve Skills\n* View Documents\n* Suspend Worker\n\n---\n\n# SERVICE MANAGEMENT\n\nCRUD:\n\n* Categories\n* Services\n* Pricing\n\n---\n\n# BOOKING MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Booking List\n* Booking Detail\n* Assign Worker\n* Status Tracking\n\n---\n\n# PAYMENT MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Transactions\n* Refund Requests\n* Revenue Reports\n\n---\n\n# AI MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* AI Models\n* AI Inference Logs\n* AI Training Data\n* AI Recommendations\n* Knowledge Base\n\n---\n\n# KNOWLEDGE BASE\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Upload Documents\n* Manage Documents\n* Search Documents\n* View Embeddings\n\n---\n\n# DEVOPS MONITORING\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Deployment Logs\n* System Logs\n* Error Monitoring\n* AI Latency Dashboard\n\n---\n\n# SETTINGS MODULE\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Dark Mode\n* Language\n* Notification Settings\n* Security Settings\n* Change Password\n* Privacy Settings\n* Delete Account\n\n---\n\nGenerate:\n\n1. Full Android Screen Flow\n2. Navigation Architecture\n3. Wireframes\n4. High Fidelity UI Layouts\n5. Material Design 3 Components\n6. Jetpack Compose Screen Structure\n7. User Journey\n8. Empty States\n9. Loading States\n10. Error States\n11. Success States\n12. Modern SaaS Mobile Design\n\nCreate all screens in detail and make the design production-ready.\n\n"
    items {
      item {
        text_block {
          content: "---\ntype: \"feature\"\ntitle: \"Build an Android app\"\nicon: \"android_color\"\n---\n\n"
        }
      }
    }
    items {
      text: "Act as a Senior Android UI/UX Designer and Senior Android Developer.\n\nGenerate a complete Android application UI design using Material Design 3 for the project:\n\n# AI-Powered Cleaning Service Booking Platform\n\nA mobile application that allows customers to book cleaning services, workers to accept jobs, and administrators to manage the entire platform. The system integrates AI Chatbot, AI Worker Recommendation, Online Payment, Real-time Notifications, GPS Tracking, and Authentication.\n\n## Design Requirements\n\n* Platform: Android\n* Design System: Material Design 3\n* Style: Modern, Professional, Clean, Similar to Grab, Uber, Airbnb and Shopee\n* Responsive Mobile UI\n* Support Dark Mode\n* Smooth animations\n* Production-ready design\n* Use realistic data\n* Generate UI hierarchy and screen layout descriptions\n* Generate Jetpack Compose UI structure for each screen\n\nPrimary Color: #2563EB\n\nSecondary Color: #10B981\n\nAccent Color: #F59E0B\n\n---\n\n# USER ROLES\n\n1. Client\n2. Worker\n3. Admin\n\n---\n\n# AUTHENTICATION MODULE\n\nCreate screens:\n\n1. Splash Screen\n2. Onboarding Screen (3 Slides)\n3. Login Screen\n4. Register Screen\n5. Forgot Password Screen\n6. OTP Verification Screen\n7. Reset Password Screen\n\nInclude:\n\n* Validation states\n* Loading states\n* Error states\n* Success states\n\n---\n\n# CLIENT APPLICATION\n\nBottom Navigation:\n\n* Home\n* Bookings\n* AI Chat\n* Notifications\n* Profile\n\n---\n\n# HOME SCREEN\n\nSections:\n\n* Welcome Header\n* Search Bar\n* Promotional Banner Carousel\n* Service Categories Grid\n* Popular Services\n* Nearby Workers\n* AI Recommended Workers\n* Special Offers\n\nService Categories:\n\n* House Cleaning\n* Deep Cleaning\n* Sofa Cleaning\n* Carpet Cleaning\n* Office Cleaning\n* Air Conditioner Cleaning\n\n---\n\n# SERVICE DETAIL SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Service Image\n* Service Name\n* Description\n* Price\n* Duration\n* Reviews\n* Ratings\n* Book Now Button\n\n---\n\n# CREATE BOOKING