e dedicated worker screens.\n\nWorker Bottom Navigation:\n\n* Dashboard\n* Jobs\n* Schedule\n* Wallet\n* Profile\n\n---\n\n# WORKER DASHBOARD\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Today\'s Earnings\n* Weekly Earnings\n* Monthly Earnings\n* Rating\n* Completed Jobs\n\nCharts:\n\n* Earnings Chart\n* Performance Chart\n\n---\n\n# WORKER JOB LIST\n\nTabs:\n\n* New Jobs\n* Accepted\n* In Progress\n* Completed\n\nActions:\n\n* Accept Job\n* Reject Job\n\n---\n\n# WORKER JOB DETAIL\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Customer Information\n* Address\n* Route Map\n* Service Details\n\nActions:\n\n* Start Job\n* Complete Job\n* Upload Before/After Images\n\n---\n\n# WORKER SCHEDULE SCREEN\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Calendar View\n* Upcoming Jobs\n* Availability Toggle\n\n---\n\n# WORKER WALLET SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Balance\n* Earnings\n* Withdraw Button\n* Transaction History\n\n---\n\n# WORKER PROFILE SCREEN\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Avatar\n* Identity Verification\n* Skills\n* Certificates\n* Ratings\n* Reviews\n\n---\n\n# ADMIN APPLICATION\n\nCreate admin dashboard screens.\n\n---\n\n# ADMIN DASHBOARD\n\nDisplay:\n\n* Total Users\n* Total Workers\n* Total Bookings\n* Revenue\n* AI Requests\n\nCharts:\n\n* Revenue Trend\n* Booking Trend\n* User Growth\n\n---\n\n# USER MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Search\n* Filter\n* User Detail\n* Ban User\n* Activate User\n\n---\n\n# WORKER MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Verify Worker\n* Approve Skills\n* View Documents\n* Suspend Worker\n\n---\n\n# SERVICE MANAGEMENT\n\nCRUD:\n\n* Categories\n* Services\n* Pricing\n\n---\n\n# BOOKING MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Booking List\n* Booking Detail\n* Assign Worker\n* Status Tracking\n\n---\n\n# PAYMENT MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Transactions\n* Refund Requests\n* Revenue Reports\n\n---\n\n# AI MANAGEMENT\n\nFeatures:\n\n* AI Models\n* AI Inference Logs\n* AI Training Data\n* AI Recommendations\n* Knowledge Base\n\n---\n\n# KNOWLEDGE BASE\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Upload Documents\n* Manage Documents\n* Search Documents\n* View Embeddings\n\n---\n\n# DEVOPS